30:54.983 --> 30:56.855
- It sounded like Mom.

30:59.292 --> 31:00.641
- That was Dad, yep.
- That was definitely Dad.

31:03.035 --> 31:05.254
- What is going on?
- I have no idea.

31:05.298 --> 31:06.865
Hey, are you guys okay?

31:06.908 --> 31:08.954
- Otra más, otra más.
- Vamo, vamo!

31:11.739 --> 31:13.262
- Where are the workers?

31:14.176 --> 31:15.743
- The contractor
stole our money.

31:15.786 --> 31:18.137
- What?
- Just the deposit.

31:18.180 --> 31:20.182
- Mami, Papi, I'm so sorry.

31:20.226 --> 31:21.836
- No, no, no, it's okay.
You know why?

31:21.880 --> 31:24.099
Because we are the Garcias.

31:24.143 --> 31:26.058
- Somos los Garcias and we're
gonna do it ourselves.

31:26.101 --> 31:27.886
- Exactly.
- The parts that we can.

31:27.929 --> 31:29.017
- Vamos, Papi.
- Vamos, yeah.

31:29.061 --> 31:31.193
- Your turn first.
Go ahead.

31:31.237 --> 31:34.631
- Hey, you got another one
of those?

31:34.675 --> 31:37.939
- We have one for everyone,
Mamita.

31:37.983 --> 31:39.288
You ready?
- Yeah.

31:39.332 --> 31:40.681
- Take it.
It's heavy.

31:40.724 --> 31:43.205
- Careful.

31:43.249 --> 31:44.250
Oh, you won't be able
to hold this.

31:44.293 --> 31:46.034
- Be careful!

31:46.078 --> 31:47.731
- Come on, Mama.

31:47.775 --> 31:49.864
- Garciadiggers, huh?
- That's right.

31:49.908 --> 31:52.258
- Take that!
- There you go, baby!

31:52.301 --> 31:53.259
Look at that!
- Yes!

31:56.088 --> 31:57.828
- Me too, me too, me too.

31:57.872 --> 31:58.917
- You get it, Mom!

31:58.960 --> 32:00.179
- Yeah, hit it hard,
hit it hard.

32:00.222 --> 32:02.224
- Whoo!
- Vamos, vamos.

32:02.268 --> 32:03.399
Mateo, let's do it!

32:03.443 --> 32:04.966
All right, all right, Mateo,
let's go!

32:05.010 --> 32:06.968
All right, here we--
Oh, come on.

32:07.012 --> 32:08.361
You need to start working out.
- Hold on, hold on, okay?

32:08.404 --> 32:09.753
- You need to start
working out.

32:09.797 --> 32:11.190
- You have to pick it up!

32:11.233 --> 32:13.018
- Come on, Papi.
You need some muscles.

32:15.759 --> 32:16.935
- Oh, my God.

32:19.328 --> 32:20.721
- Whoo!

32:26.379 --> 32:29.251
-  What is that?

32:30.426 --> 32:32.689
Oh, what's that smell?

32:32.733 --> 32:33.821
- Wait, wait, wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait.

32:33.864 --> 32:34.909
Mateo, give me a hand here.
Come on.

32:34.953 --> 32:35.910
Watch it, watch it, watch it.

32:40.262 --> 32:42.786
- Everybody get out,
get out, get out, get out!

32:48.444 --> 32:50.838
- The thing is, Juliet, you're
one of only two board members

32:50.881 --> 32:52.100
who asked
to see the financials.

32:52.144 --> 32:53.362
- Yes, Tom,
and Piper's on the phone

32:53.406 --> 32:54.450
with the other one right now.

32:54.494 --> 32:56.017
- I just want
to know what's going on.

32:56.061 --> 32:57.671
- Oh, you know that I know
that you know what's going on.

32:57.714 --> 32:59.238
- Okay, well,
then who asked you to do it?

32:59.281 --> 33:01.240
- Mark Logan?
- Mark Logan?

33:01.283 --> 33:02.719
Did he say why?

33:02.763 --> 33:04.852
- An emergency board meeting?
- When?

33:04.895 --> 33:05.984
- Oh, God.

33:06.027 --> 33:07.507
- Juliet,
I gotta call you back.

33:07.550 --> 33:09.161
Are you okay? What's happening?
Do you need a doctor?

33:09.204 --> 33:11.859
- What?
No, no, it's not that.

33:11.902 --> 33:13.426
In order to call
an emergency board meeting,

33:13.469 --> 33:15.254
you need two members
to make a motion.

33:15.297 --> 33:17.430
We already know
that one of them is Mark Logan.

33:17.473 --> 33:20.172
Now, ask yourself,
who is the one person

33:20.215 --> 33:22.000
who would do something
that underhanded

33:22.043 --> 33:23.088
at a time like this?

33:23.131 --> 33:25.090
- We called
all the other board members.

33:25.133 --> 33:27.353
- No, we haven't.

33:28.745 --> 33:31.139
- Oh.
- Yes.

33:39.017 --> 33:41.019
- Oh, you gotta be kidding me.

33:45.240 --> 33:46.807
- Can I come in?

33:49.244 --> 33:51.246
Paparazzi have the bakery
staked out.

33:53.031 --> 33:56.338
Natalie, she's getting
picked on at school.

33:57.470 --> 34:00.299
There's some sort of trouble
at Noa's company.

34:01.430 --> 34:05.260
And me...I'm fighting
with my family.

34:05.304 --> 34:07.306
Is that what you wanted?

34:12.963 --> 34:18.012
- What I wanted was to stop
losing potential clients.

34:18.056 --> 34:20.101
What I wanted was
to be seen for who I am

34:20.145 --> 34:22.103
and not some internet meme.

34:24.801 --> 34:26.368
You think I wanted to hurt you?

34:28.152 --> 34:30.329
I don't know what's worse,

34:30.371 --> 34:32.112
that you could be
that narcissistic

34:32.157 --> 34:34.333
or that you think I'd actually
do something like that.

34:35.985 --> 34:38.076
That might've not been
your intention,

34:38.119 --> 34:39.773
but that's what's happening.

34:39.815 --> 34:41.382
And it all started
with that interview.

34:41.427 --> 34:42.384
- Okay, what do you want me
to do?

34:42.428 --> 34:43.907
- Help me stop it.

34:43.951 --> 34:45.257
Go to the press,
tell them the truth.

34:45.300 --> 34:46.822
- I did tell them the truth!

34:48.347 --> 34:52.481
Everything I said
is exactly what happened.

34:52.525 --> 34:54.918
Now, you may not like
how the truth makes you look,

34:54.962 --> 34:57.399
but mirrors can be cruel
sometimes.

35:01.142 --> 35:05.581
- I shouldn't have come.
- At last, we agree.

35:24.383 --> 35:26.559
- Hey, Daniel!

35:32.652 --> 35:34.262
- Well,
this doesn't look good.

35:41.182 --> 35:45.143
- Does Noa know you're here?
- Dude, are you following me?

35:45.186 --> 35:47.449
- They're putting together
an emergency board meeting,

35:47.493 --> 35:49.059
and at that board meeting,

35:49.103 --> 35:50.452
they're gonna vote

35:50.496 --> 35:53.977
to remove you as president
of your company.

35:58.330 --> 36:00.984
- Remove me?

36:01.028 --> 36:02.029
Who would do that?

36:04.510 --> 36:07.034
My father.

36:10.994 --> 36:12.996
- Which one's better in bed?

36:38.152 --> 36:41.416
- Hey. I missed you.
- I missed you too.

36:42.983 --> 36:44.245
- Mm.

36:44.289 --> 36:45.246
In other words--
- I wanted to--

36:45.290 --> 36:46.247
- Oh.

36:46.291 --> 36:48.293
Can I go first?

36:48.336 --> 36:50.120
- Yeah.

36:50.164 --> 36:52.122
I just wanted
to tell you something

36:52.166 --> 36:53.950
before you found out
from somebody else.

36:53.994 --> 36:56.257
- You punched Kurt Malick.

36:56.301 --> 36:57.476
- I did.

36:58.999 --> 37:00.218
I'm sorry.

37:01.610 --> 37:03.482
It's just a lot.

37:05.135 --> 37:08.400
And I can't believe how well
you handle the pressure

37:08.443 --> 37:13.492
day after day, especially
when they make it so personal.

37:13.535 --> 37:16.886
It feels like you can't--
- Breathe?

37:16.930 --> 37:18.453
- Yeah.

37:23.328 --> 37:26.026
- Daniel, I've had my whole
life to deal with this chaos.

37:26.069 --> 37:28.594
You've had, what, a month?

37:28.637 --> 37:33.163
The truth is, it's not really
fair to you

37:33.207 --> 37:34.600
or your family.

37:44.087 --> 37:46.394
- What's going on?

37:52.052 --> 37:53.880
- Let's take a walk.

37:55.969 --> 37:59.407
- Mrs. Howe,
of course, of course.

37:59.451 --> 38:00.930
Okay, bye-bye.

38:04.064 --> 38:05.457
Suspension.
- Oh, my God.

38:05.500 --> 38:07.937
- But it could've easily
been expulsion.

38:07.981 --> 38:09.069
- I know, I know.

38:09.112 --> 38:10.331
And it will never happen again,
I swear.

38:10.375 --> 38:12.942
- That's right, it won't.

38:12.986 --> 38:17.033
And Amy--did you know she has a
history of disciplinary issues?

38:17.077 --> 38:19.906
- She doesn't have a history
of disciplinary issues, okay?

38:19.949 --> 38:21.603
She got caught TP'ing
the school mascot

38:21.647 --> 38:23.344
with, like, five other girls.

38:23.388 --> 38:26.521
- Oh, so then you admit that
she's been in trouble before.

38:26.565 --> 38:29.263
- Okay?
- "Okay?"

38:29.307 --> 38:30.569
Then you'll understand why

38:30.612 --> 38:33.441
I am forbidding you
from seeing her anymore.

38:33.485 --> 38:35.269
- Uh-uh!

38:43.364 --> 38:44.496
- Well, the gas leak
is repaired,

38:44.539 --> 38:46.541
but that's not your problem.

38:46.585 --> 38:47.890
The problem is, it looks like

38:47.934 --> 38:50.328
