all throughout these walls.

38:50.371 --> 38:51.329
- Asbestos?

38:51.372 --> 38:52.547
- It has to be removed

38:52.591 --> 38:54.157
and the building's gonna have
to be certified.

38:54.201 --> 38:55.681
- How--how long will it take?

38:55.724 --> 38:59.685
- I'd say your bakery can
reopen in about 10 to 12 weeks.

39:01.469 --> 39:03.123
- He wanted to hire me?

39:03.166 --> 39:06.126
- Yeah, why are you acting
so surprised?

39:06.169 --> 39:07.649
He knows how to seek talent,
right?

39:07.693 --> 39:10.435
Consider it.
He's the real deal.

39:12.132 --> 39:14.656
And so are you.

39:16.397 --> 39:19.574
Anyway, just wanted
to let you know.

39:22.316 --> 39:24.144
- To hell with him.

39:24.187 --> 39:27.234
He's wrong about you.

39:27.277 --> 39:29.236
Why would I want
to work with him?

39:31.281 --> 39:34.284
- I appreciate it...

39:34.328 --> 39:36.286
but it's over.

39:39.246 --> 39:42.031
MC Cubano is over.

39:51.476 --> 39:54.435
- My father's trying
to take my company from me.

39:54.479 --> 39:56.698
- What?

39:56.742 --> 40:00.093
- There's a reason why I don't
talk about him a lot.

40:00.136 --> 40:03.444
It's a very painful
relationship.

40:03.488 --> 40:05.664
He only married my mother
because she was pregnant,

40:05.707 --> 40:11.409
and then when she got sick,
he completely abandoned her.

40:13.541 --> 40:16.326
- I was emancipated from him
when I was 16

40:16.370 --> 40:19.547
but not before
I started my company.

40:19.591 --> 40:22.289
- With his money.
- Exactly.

40:22.332 --> 40:25.466
- And ever since then, he's
been able to sit on my board

40:25.510 --> 40:29.252
and have a piece of every
single one of my successes.

40:29.296 --> 40:30.689
- Okay, but it's still
your company.

40:30.732 --> 40:33.213
Why do this?
- Exactly, why?

40:33.256 --> 40:36.303
Why would a father do that
to his daughter?

40:36.346 --> 40:38.305
I don't know.

40:38.348 --> 40:41.047
All I know is that
he senses I'm vulnerable

40:41.090 --> 40:43.092
and he's coming for me.

40:46.618 --> 40:49.795
So what are you gonna do?

40:49.838 --> 40:51.710
- I'm gonna do
what I always do.

40:51.753 --> 40:53.233
I'm gonna fight.

40:53.276 --> 40:55.540
I'm gonna fly to New York,
Los Angeles, and London

40:55.583 --> 40:57.367
and meet with
every single board member

40:57.411 --> 41:00.588
and convince them not
to believe my father's lies.

41:00.632 --> 41:03.591
- You're not only gonna fight,
you're gonna win.

41:03.635 --> 41:05.854
I'm here for you every step
of the way.

41:05.898 --> 41:08.727
I'll go home and pack my bags.

41:10.380 --> 41:13.688
- You're so kind, Daniel.
That's very sweet of you.

42:00.692 --> 42:02.476
- What are you saying?

42:04.696 --> 42:08.482
- I can't be distracted
when I go on this trip.
